<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-08 00:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0406 &Cx1f; tth-z
u s BC-FBC-THIEL-COLUMN-SPI &LR;      10-08 0851
