r s BC-BBA-RANGERS-CLUTCH-TE     10-08 0407
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BBA-RANGERS-CLUTCH-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
RANGERS SQUANDER OPPORTUNITIES IN CRITICAL FIFTH INNING
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JOHNNY PAUL 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ Right-hander Rick Helling provided the Rangers an
opportunity to return to The Ballpark in Arlington with the
best-of-five Division Series against the Yankees square at a
victory apiece.
</P>
