   FCC-CABLE (Washington) _ The FCC relaxes significantly the rules
governing cable ownership concentration, just two months after
relaxing similar rules on broadcast ownership. Friday's step will
allow AT&AMP;T to complete its takeover of Mediaone with only marginal
divestitures. 1,000 words. By Steven Labaton.
</P>
