<P>
   &QL;  PA Contract Awards States News Service Washington, October 8
-- Modjeski and Masters Inc. of Mechanicsburg won a $300,000
contract from the Army in Philadelphia, Pa., for construction
services.
</P>
<P>
   Litton Systems Inc. of Williamsport won a $90,573 contract from
Defense Supply Center in Columbus, Ohio, for electrical and
electronic equipment.
