   UNDATED _ It was a case of back-to-the-drawing-board for vehicle
designers at Ford Motor Co. The result: a drastically redesigned
Ford Taurus for 2000, part of an all-out effort to recapture the
momentum this car lost when it received a radical redesign in 1996.
By G. CHAMBERS WILLIAMS III. Story will move in ``l'' lifestyle
category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   RELIGION-JONES-COLUMN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Former President Carter has been teaching Sunday
school since he was 18. He even taught in Washington when he was
president. And he's still at it. Each week, Carter prepares a
lesson, using his Bible and Scripture references recommended by his
denomination. Then he goes to his home church in Plains, Ga., each
Sunday to teach a class for adults. All of us are looking for some
answers. And this man of faith, very humble in his own way, seems
to be on the right track. By JIM JONES. Story has moved in ``l''
lifestyle category. &QL; 
