she said, ``I just say, `Look to your own lives. Look to yourself,
everybody. Fix yourselves, and keep your problems to yourself.'''
That answer sets the tone for Russell's biography. It gives notice
very early on that the former Claudia Alta Taylor isn't about to
spill any personal or political beans; that she has spent a
lifetime protecting her family from public scrutiny, and this
effort by Russell will probably not get past her guard. By ART
CHAPMAN. Story has moved in ``e'' arts and entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   TV-PERKINS-COLUMN &QL;
</P>
