</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    GORE FIGHTING TO AVOID A REBUFF AT AFL-CIO CONVENTION
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories for release
Sunday, Oct. 10.
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
