<SLUG> BC-CARS-WILLIAMS-COLUMN-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
FORD INTRODUCES DRASTICALLY REDESIGNED TAURUS FOR 2000
</HEADLINE>
 
(EDS: Accompanied by CARS-GLANCE) (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By G. CHAMBERS WILLIAMS 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   It was a case of back-to-the-drawing-board for vehicle designers
at Ford Motor Co.
</P>
<P>
   The result: a drastically redesigned Ford Taurus for 2000, part
