   Here are the stories New York Times editors are planning for
Page 1, Saturday, October 9, 1999. The NYT frontpage advisory, with
layout description, will move by 7:30 p.m. ET. The N.Y. Times News
Service Night Supervisor is Pat Ryan; phone: (888) 346-9867;
