<P>
   (The story is scheduled to move by 8 p.m. ET.)
</P>
<P>
   (Center right)
</P>
<P>
   XEROX-EARNINGS (Undated) _ Shares of Xerox plunged Friday after
the company said its third-quarter earnings would fall because of
increased competition and lower productivity. By Claudia H.
Deutsch.
</P>
<P>
   (The story has moved.)
