midsize sedan with an attractive, roomy interior that's loaded with
features. It also drives quite well. Nothing spectacular, but
certainly a lot of car for the money. The bottom line is really the
story here. By BOB GOLFEN. Story will move in the ``L'' category. &QL; 
 &QL;
